reviewText:
I like cheesy movies. My faves are MST3K's. I bought these Euro Trash: Triple Features because I thought they would be fun to make fun of and they do not disappoint. If you want some flashbacks to the 70's, or love dubbed Euro Trash movies, this item is for you. If you enjoy films that are short on plot and cohesiveness, this is just what you are looking for.

Many a time I have yelled at the screen at the conclusion of a feature, "That's not a movie!" I am really enjoying them!
these movies are great i love gore gore gore gore gore gore gore night rider! it is worth it to get faceless alone
